  npcName: The Elder
  npcPotrait: {fileID: 7168534318667288126, guid: aa50aaec02f89434aa6f6b71fbe0f192, type: 3}
  dialogueLines:
  - 'Hello '
  - 'I am a quest giver baba '
  - 'Do you want a Quest ? '
  - 'Great !  '
  - I knew you are a hardworking baalak.
  - I expect better from you
  - Jaude next time .
  - Goodluck with the task.
  - Great Job arjunnnnnnn . Proud of you.
  - "You\u2019ve learned how money is earned."
  - Now learn how it leaves.
  - "Go to the market. Don\u2019t calculate. Observe."
  - As expect Arjun , this will help you a lot !
  - Understanding taxes is very important to power up
  - 'For securing your future , understanding investments is as important as anything
    else '
  - Use your market app in your phone and explore the market
  - Buy and sell stocks for better understanding
  - There is no other investment like stocks
  - Great Job Arjun !
  - To know how todays system works you need to understand how it works in communities
    too
  - 'Talk to the Bhishi community in the park to understand it better '
  - Great Job Arjun !
